OL,3,GOPINIONCWhen playout goes badly wrong
OL,4,
OL,5,GWIDER CONTEXT
OL,7,FWe understand that Red Bee's contract
OL,8,Fto provide playout and media management
OL,9,Ffor BBC TV channels ` such as BBC One,
OL,10,FBBC Two, BBC Three, BBC Four, CBeebies
OL,11,Fand CBBC ` expires next year.
OL,13,FRed Bee is responsible for the playout
OL,14,Fof "network" versions of BBC One and
OL,15,FBBC Two. These are broadcast to viewers
OL,16,Fin England for most of the day.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,148,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14705
SC,0005
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F147A1776604038
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCWhen playout goes badly wrong
OL,4,
OL,5,FNorthern Ireland, Scotland and Wales
OL,6,Fhave their own versions of BBC One,
OL,7,Fwhich largely take the network schedule
OL,8,Fbut have their own programming at
OL,9,Ftimes, and their own continuity for
OL,10,Fmuch of the day.
OL,12,FThere's a similar arrangement on BBC
OL,13,FTwo for Northern Ireland and Wales.
OL,15,FWith further cost-cutting measures in
OL,16,Fthe pipeline at the Corporation, there
OL,17,Fis an opportunity here to bring back
OL,18,Fin-house vital services such as playout
OL,19,Fand media management and utilise
OL,20,Fexisting BBC playout centres in
OL,21,FBelfast, Glasgow and Cardiff.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,148,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14706
SC,0006
