OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F147A1776604038
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCWhen playout goes badly wrong
OL,4,
OL,5,FRed Bee could play out tailored
OL,6,Fjunctions to each nation and deal with
OL,7,Ftheir schedule changes. Such a solution
OL,8,Fis already in place on "the other side"
OL,9,Ffor UTV and ITV 1 Wales (not to mention
OL,10,Feach ITV English region).
OL,12,FBut we'd argue this could be done more
OL,13,Fcost-effectively by making use of the
OL,14,FBBC's existing in-house playout
OL,15,Foperations.
OL,17,FTechnological advances mean location is
OL,18,Fno longer the obstacle it once was.
OL,19,FPlayout for BBC Parliament for example
OL,20,Fis managed by the BBC in Belfast.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,148,140,200,120,0,100
PN,14707
SC,0007
CT,3,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F147A1776604038
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G7/7
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCWhen playout goes badly wrong
OL,4,
OL,5,FWhilst Red Bee certainly doesn't have
OL,6,Fan entirely clean copybook when it
OL,7,Fcomes to playout errors, blunders such
OL,8,Fas this evening's on BBC One Scotland
OL,9,Fdo damage to the reputation of internal
OL,10,Fplayout operations.
OL,12,FAnd our perception is that BBC Scotland
OL,13,Fis more error-prone than is desirable.
OL,15,FHopefully managers at Pacific Quay are
OL,16,Ftrying to establish exactly what
OL,17,Fhappened this evening and will put
OL,18,Fmeasures in place to ensure there's no
OL,19,Frepetition.
OL,23,EPub: 18-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
